history.content:
The EECS Department on campus wants to hear your opinions regarding your classes, how much you are enjoying EECS, and what you want improved. This is a student organized and administered survey. 
Speak your mind about academic honesty, curriculum, study spaces, student life, etc. There will be a random drawing for Amazon gift certificates. 
bit.ly/EECS2015survey
The survey should take about 15 minutes. 
Leaders from HKN, UPE, AWE, CSUA, IEEE, Blueprint, and OSTEM will read what you write and will present the information collected from this survey at the ongoing Undergraduate Social Hours which all are invited to attend. 
Rest assured that your response is completely anonymous and cannot be linked to you in any way, and your voice will be heard. Don't forget to show this with your friends!
history.subject: Tell us your opinion! Take this important survey!
